{
  "stem": "26022.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what I ever became-- I don't mean professionally, but as a person-- I owe, first of all, to my parents, but then to a large extent to this magnificent group of women who were knowledgeable and capable and sort of maybe this-- if I could compare that-- the suffragette generation.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were instilled with a great sense of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] perfectionism.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Women can do anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they can do it better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they have to apply themselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When I think of today's schools here, this, this lack of motivation and whatnot, that didn't exist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was very easy to be told not to come back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the-- from-- there were eight grades.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And from grade one to grade eight-- well, if I tell you we were 17 when we graduated in my class, which was one section.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other section had some 20-odd girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I think we were under 50, or not much over 40, when we graduated that year in 1939.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But we had a wonderful time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was not all, all studies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had extracurricular activities like lab work on a voluntary basis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We also had tennis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- that was in the afternoon, after school let out after three.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of course, we had school on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was every school still had a half day in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had eight years of Latin and five years of English and-- British English-- and lots of physics and chemistry, for which I was not very well-suited.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But you know, you put your nose in the book.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there were no excuses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I graduated with fairly good marks, if you want to see my [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It, it is something like the baccalaureate program internationally.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
